Zakrzewko  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Kozłowo, within Nidzica County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-east of Kozłowo,  south-west of Nidzica, and  south of the regional capital Olsztyn.
